compilation: 
premake4 gmake; make; ./A2
worked on computer gl13.student.cs

manual:
-cannot scale to less than 0.1f
-near plane cannot be greater than far plane
-far plane cannot be less than near plane
-eye is at (0, 0, -15)
-to draw viewport, the mouse is only allowed to drag in down/right directions
-viewport is limited by the size of the window
-model coordinate color: x=red, y=green, z=blue
-world coordinate color: x=yellow, y=magenta, z=cyan

